 <p class=\"item-credits\">guvendemir</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Amidst widespread speculation, the return of President Trump as commander-in-chief could threaten earnings growth in the defense industry in 2025. Analysts seeing it this way point to these items on the perceived Trump agenda:</p> <ul> <li>Hardball negotiations with defense</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1176850442/image_1176850442.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741802-taking-defensive-stance-on-defense-stocks", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 20:15:00"}, {"id": "4741789", "title": "Celsius Is Not A Bargain Despite 70% Share Price Drop", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man giving energy drink to tired young woman sitting at gym\" data-id=\"1705909279\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705909279/image_1705909279.jpg?io=getty-c-w240